    "title": "The Data Ethics Canvas",
    "displayTitle": "The Data Ethics Canvas",
    "body": "<p>The Data Ethics Canvas helps teams to have a guided discussion to identify the positive and negative impacts of their data project on people and society. It's a tool for anyone who collects, shares or uses data. It helps identify and manage ethical issues - in both the promotion of positive outcomes and mitigation of negative outcomes.</p>",
